articles.description: The six limited-overs matches in Sydney and Canberra have almost sold out
articles.content: The prospect of the opening Test between Australia and India remaining in Adelaide has received a boost with South Australia to come out of its strict Covid-19 lockdown three days early on Saturday.… [+1496 chars]
